title: Sebastian Coe - Wikipedia
snippet: Sebastian Newbold Coe, Baron Coe, ... and retired track and field athlete. As a middle-distance runner, Coe won four Olympic medals, including 1500 metres gold medals at the Olympic Games in 1980 and 1984....

title: Lord Sebastian Coe - Michael Cassel Group
snippet: Lord Coe is the President of the International Association of Athletics Federations (IAAF) and the Executive Chairman of CSM Sport & Entertainment. As an athlete he won Olympic gold medals in the 1500 metres in 1980 and 1984 and set 12 middle-distance world records...
